item.description: I'm not one for heavy duty hiking. I like leisurely strolls with a lot of swimming for the boys and running in the woods. Seeing as how Dave had to postpone the walk at Northwood Meadows I am still planning on taking Shemp and DeeJay that day if anyone cares to join us. I am going to do two loops around the lake with a lot of water time.
